data.text: @adoringtay for some reason the "Twilight" thing has been hard to shake off for all three of them, to be quite frank.   I think Taylor has comedic chops and flourished in things like the aforementioned "Scream Queens" and "Cuckoo," where he's the best part of the show.  I wish him the best!
@littlelostsunny He hasn't done as many projects as the others . And unlike them he isn't pushed in the media . His work is either blasted by critics or ignored.
@adoringtay He has not done anything even close to award-worthy in film.  Loved him in Scream Queens though.
@littlelostsunny How did vilifying Taylor for a role he played become a thing? Here it is 2018 and it's the same tired routine.  #eracism
